Muta Mfg.

Co, say e don establish subsidiary for Britain wey be sey e go produce electric, plus one ceramic condenser.

Tokyo wey be ceramic capacitor say e buy plant for Plymouth.

Di company no talk tok about di price of goods, or capitalisation figures.

Mutad say however, e go invest like 1.4 billion yen ($9.9 million) inside di new company.

De wan begin process for April.

Di company wey get European foothold, Murata Europe Management G.B.

H. For Germany, dem talk sey di latest one wey dey happen na to meet demand for electricity for inside European Community countries before di start of di unified market by 1992.

Mutai expects sale at di unit of about 1.5 billion yen for di first year.

